  "name": "RPlog_A_Random_Visit",
  "title": "A Random Visit",
  "summary": "The Republic officer Rasi lands aboard the cruise vessel Angry Rancor over Ord Mantell and, with barely concealed distaste for the greeting protocol droid, seeks out the Jordains. He is met by the cadet Tarin and by Inanna Jordain, who wryly corrects Rasi's assumption that she is the junior sister -- she is six years the elder. Settling in, the three fall into a wide-ranging conversation about the Task Force, recent light engagements at Nak Shimor and other strategic points, and the perennial Imperial habit of \"offering help\" to worlds in need as a pretext for control. Tarin, eager for action and to \"blast some Imps,\" floats the idea of the military stepping in early to deal with the Dac crisis on its own, while acknowledging limited resources make it unlikely to be approved. Inanna, thoughtful and slightly guarded, defers the military planning to the soldiers and reassures them that nothing is owed in return, the visit ending on cordial, exploratory terms.",
